  <h2>Summary</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Beets are a cool-season, direct-sow crop.</li>
    <li>Sow near last frost when soil is workable.</li>
    <li>Use days-to-maturity + first frost for fall cutoffs.</li>
    <li>Hard freezes at 32°F (0°C) end unprotected finishing.</li>
  </ol>
</section>
